com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.impl

Class WorkerShardTask<I,O,C extends WorkerContext<O>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.impl.WorkerShardTask<I,O,C>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of input values consumed by the worker
    O - type of output values produced by the worker
    C - type of context required by the worker
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IncrementalTaskWithContext, IncrementalTask, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapOnlyShardTask, MapShardTask, MergeShardTask, ReduceShardTask, SortShardTask

    public abstract class WorkerShardTask<I,O,C extends WorkerContext<O>>
extends Object
implements IncrementalTaskWithContext
    Base class for the specific MR stage workers. Each subclass is responsible to set the context on its input, output, and worker.
    Author:
    ohler@google.com (Christian Ohler)
